      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 10.0,
      "text": "It is currently 13 degrees and cloudy in Berlin-Tempelhof."
    },
    {
      "end": 17.715,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 14.06,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a71a7c635f7"
      ],
      "end": 36.393,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 17.715,
      "text": "The physical backbone of artificial intelligence is expanding in Texas. Coherent has broken ground on an expanded manufacturing facility in Sherman to produce lasers and optical components. The site will utilize six-inch indium phosphide to create the semiconductors that wire high-performance AI systems together."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "afe6577af9c",
        "aed7928cde3"
      ],
      "end": 59.537,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 36.393,
      "text": "While hardware scales, frontier models are moving into direct government and engineering workflows. The UK government is partnering with Google DeepMind to build an AI-powered prototype that accelerates housing planning and construction decisions. At the same time, Moonshot AI has released Kimi K2.7 Code, an open-source agentic model designed to automate software engineering tasks."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a375d166572"
      ],
      "end": 73.342,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s8",
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 59.537,
      "text": "This shift toward specialized automation extends into the financial sector. NVIDIA has released technical guidance for building foundation models that use transaction data, such as swipes and transfers, as behavioral signals for financial intelligence."
    },
    {
      "end": 76.185,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 73.342,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 81.057,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 76.185,
      "text": "This afternoon will remain cloudy with temperatures between 20 and 24 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 84.305,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 81.057,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 90.802,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s13"
      ],
      "start": 84.305,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 101.359,
      "id": "p9",
      "index": 9,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s14"
      ],
      "start": 90.802,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
